title: Grateful Dead Live at Rosemont Horizon on 1989-04-11
description:
Set 1

Shakedown Street, Little Red Rooster, Friend Of The Devil, Victim Or The Crime, Built To Last, We Can Run But We Can't Hide, Memphis Blues, Deal

Set 2

Samson & Delilah, Crazy Fingers, Playin' In The Band-> Terrapin Station-> Drums-> Jam-> Gimme Some Lovin'-> Standing On the Moon, Throwing Stones-> Not Fade Away, E: U.S. Blues
